<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>STARRY-S' Blog</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/</link><description>This is my cool site</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>hxstarrys@gmail.com (STARRY-S)</managingEditor><webMaster>hxstarrys@gmail.com (STARRY-S)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Jan 2023 11:05:02 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.starry-s.moe/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>入手一台家用级 APC UPS</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2023/apc-ups/</link><pubDate>Sun, 08 Jan 2023 11:05:02 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2023/apc-ups/</guid><description>&lt;p>为了让咱的 NAS 长时间稳定运行，斥巨资买了一台 APC BK650M2-CH，在 Arch Wiki 上看 APC 的 UPS 对 Linux 的支持比较友好，于是挑了个最便宜的带停电自动关机的 APC UPS，防止咱啥时候忘了交电费导致停电数据受损。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hello 2023</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2023/hello-2023/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Jan 2023 01:20:31 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2023/hello-2023/</guid><description>&lt;p>2023 新年快乐。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>NAS 装机记录</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/build-nas/</link><pubDate>Sat, 12 Nov 2022 13:25:03 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/build-nas/</guid><description>&lt;p>差不多去年的这个时候尝试过用树莓派插移动硬盘的方式试探性的组装了一个 NAS，但实际上用了不到两天这个方案就被废弃掉了……&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>食虫植物种植记录 - 2022.11.06</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/carnivorous-plant-221106/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 Nov 2022 14:58:42 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/carnivorous-plant-221106/</guid><description>&lt;p>过了一个多月，多数植物的状态都有好转，期间土瓶草和几个状态很差的茅膏菜挂掉了，猪笼草新结了几个瓶子。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>月姫 -A piece of blue glass moon-</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/tsukihimi/</link><pubDate>Fri, 28 Oct 2022 20:15:42 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/tsukihimi/</guid><description>&lt;figure>
